en the Lines: Master the Subtle Elements of Fiction Writing |first = Jessica Page |last = Morrell |publisher = Writer's Digest Books |location = Cincinnati, OH |year = 2006 |page = 127 |isbn = 978-1-58297-393-7 }} * {{cite book |first = Peter |last = Selgin |title = By Cunning & Craft: Sound Advice and Practical Wisdom for fiction writers |publisher = Writer's Digest Books |location = Cincinnati, OH |year = 2007 |page = 38 |isbn = 978-1-58297-491-0 }}
